SUMMARY:Peter Black: Music at Brockwell Park Greenhouses
LOCATION:Community Greenhouses, Brockwell Park
DESCRIPTION:Peter Black is a classically-trained guitarist who appeared on Sky TVs Guitar star who was recognised for his stylistic versatility and ability to captivate audiences. We are excited to announce that he is giving a concert as part of the Herne Hill Music Festival. The concert will feature__substantial classical works by Francisco T__rrega, Jorge Morel, Barrios-Mangor__ and Villa-Lobos, as well Classical crossover arrangements of Popular music from the UK and Latin America. There will also be a taste of other musical styles like Calypso, Flamenco and Blues, along with some of Peter's own compositions.

Do not miss this chance to be mesmerised by Peter's performance that he describes__as an International Tour of Guitar Music.__
